係防暴商場刻意撞低路人 又係假新聞<br />\n<br />\n防暴係將軍澳失控 用警棍襲擊正在離開嘅路人頭部 打到頭破血流 又係假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之係假新聞<br />\n<br />\n「假新聞」萬能key<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6414f05604d9a04561a0ceabdfb9cb9e9b021e6b","tid":2352250,"uid":109713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d157f4b3f67b2c4d13efba881f1f78fc2902823","tid":2352250,"uid":152976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"同老千傾計?<br />\n對住D詐騙電話都話得閒冇野做撚佢2句<br />\n對住依個老千港共 講多句都嫌浪費生命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"真 仲有咩好傾<br />\n老千都好信嘅咩<br />\n信個個都on99"},{"pid":"98793dbb433815085cd212d7367b1ccd9f8e18b8","tid":2352250,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5404c778e3ea46b51ea8c43337099b6254c661d","tid":2352250,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff70747bc39e48fe9bb5a1afe7ed1ed4fd8c2bdd","tid":2352250,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:09:19.000Z","msg":"根本想香港收皮，拆乜嘢彈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"777:積落既屎反正比下任...緊係有咁盡得咁盡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"唔係, 林鄭只係傀儡, 唔好集中喺特首呢個傀儡位置度<br />\n中共由一開始就係想食咗香港, 就算香港收皮都要完全受控<br />\n所以點解要解決社會問題, 解決晒啲人咪得"},{"pid":"a12e06da942885dccb720fca53502d39b6ac2ca4","tid":2352250,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9071ff2ab7ba4a5025bc995ce8b5435785a339d","tid":2352250,"uid":6435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:13:11.000Z","msg":"居然重有10%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"好神奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee008af1c91bdbbbedd1e7e5a53d241977af3f9","tid":2352250,"uid":23471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"香港政府：理撚得你 我有槍 吹咩"},{"pid":"c6fce2c411d03166f77005fa79dcd50ec2a70079","tid":2