04%2F4KITBJ56QZFJPDGVOQ66XHWSW4%2F&h=fa1b1dfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/4KITBJ56QZFJPDGVOQ66XHWSW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n林鄭心戰室撥款調查 87%港青不信任政府 <br />\n學者警告：累積火藥無人拆彈<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】反送中運動許多案件去年開審，大量年輕人被濫捕濫控、重判入獄。中文大學賽馬會公共衞生及基層醫療學院訪問250名高中學生，多達87%學生表明對政府沒有信心，負責帶領研究的助理教授黎可欣昨日形容有關結果是警號，呼籲政府、社工和校長等不要視年輕人為問題，應讓他們有「平起平坐」發聲的空間；有學者亦提醒小火種有機會引致大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「謊言治港 特首早被看穿」<br />\n<br />\n中文大學賽馬會公共衞生及基層醫療學院早前獲政策創新與統籌辦事處（特首林鄭月娥解散中央政策組後成立的心戰室部門）撥款，去年疫情期間訪問了250名高中學生，了解他們對政府及社會的信任程度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XMzG1PRqBc8XU3QtQE7p7U9MTyE=/3543x2362/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SBG53BUKRJCHVDFPYHL5D6L5D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXMzG1PRqBc8XU3QtQE7p7U9MTyE%3D%2F3543x2362%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSBG53BUKRJCHVDFPYHL5D6L5D4.jpg&h=2631572d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批年輕人在反送中運動中被濫捕濫控後，近九成受訪高中學生表明不信任政府。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n缺乏平等討論機會<br />\n<br />\n本報向創新辦索取報告全文，創新辦昨晚回覆表示，有關研究報告會按既定程序處理；待評審委員會評定後，會適當處理研究報告的公佈細則。<br />\n<br />\n負責領導研究的中大。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黎可欣形容有關結果是一個警號，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n港大社會工作及社會行政學系系主任林一星在同一節目指，現時沒有平台讓年輕人發揮，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林認為調查結果顯示政府管治面對很大挑戰，年輕人及政府欠缺互信，亦無平等討論。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對一般人信任度低<br />\n<br />\n教協副會長葉建源認為政府漠視市民訴求，一意孤行，施政高度政治化，造成不公道，致中學生對政府失去信心。去年很多涉及反送中運動的年輕人被審判，更對學生造成重擊，「政府淨係強調學生有大問題，但唔聽學生意見，只係指摘，令關係惡化」。<br />\n<br />\n葉又指高中生對一般人信任度亦低，或與過去一年多社會撕裂有關，過去人與人之。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨副主席林卓廷表示，調查結。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭前年9月宣佈撤回逃犯條例草案後曾提出邀學者研究社會深層次問題，黎可欣。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nWwdpEuqNqAlS9kk_JfJHa9n7L8=/3986x2657/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QUT6PNEYAND3LN4ROZYV3J6FLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnWwdpEuqNqAlS9kk_JfJHa9n7L8%3D%2F3986x2657%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQUT6PNEYAND3LN4ROZYV3J6FLI.jpg&h=cb7b3beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ysss7EWeCQhmDGImoR5yvKxvM1k=/945x891/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VIMRNHD5W5C4VG443KBFEJTCRI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fysss7EWeCQhmDGImoR5yvKxvM1k%3D%2F945x891%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVIMRNHD5W5C4VG443KBFEJTCRI.gif&h=98e1ddbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/79DjO_bJMDkY2GorkHlZPxeKLsc=/1407x779/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XNU66QYDTNDTNJKIS6PEY3GM3A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F79DjO_bJMDkY2GorkHlZPxeKLsc%3D%2F1407x779%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXNU66QYDTNDTNJKIS6PEY3GM3A.gif&h=263a23b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"13%不正常 on99"},{"pid":"0ad168505787787c3e6ec269867c2895c62cf307","tid":2352250,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ddb42f139df52d4e210ec9a034c2a94ceaab97c","tid":2352250,"uid":14494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"責任全在_方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2oBz4Qu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2oBz4Qu.gif&h=7f037179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99b3fb1f917fab8013716d9a765c137992c1c0ca","tid":2352250,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T04:23:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗調查都知啦